name: Geographical Reach(FPO Member Detail)
query:
SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN state_name != '' THEN state_name ELSE NULL END) AS state_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN district_name != '' THEN district_name ELSE NULL END) AS district_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN block_name != '' THEN block_name ELSE NULL END) AS block_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN grampanchayat_name != '' THEN grampanchayat_name ELSE NULL END) AS grampanchayat_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN village_name != '' THEN village_name ELSE NULL END) AS village_count
FROM
    `tabFPO member details`
